  ('bookkeeper-moex-01718', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-100-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '會計上通常以「成本」（而非「清算價值」）來列示資產的價值，主要是基於：', '["會計期間假設", "繼續經營假設", "企業個體假設", "貨幣單位衡量假設"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "36c39c55491d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f7ba25d8d88a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "100230", "c": "602", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "100", "exam_name": "100年專技人員高考建築師、技師、第2次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01719', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-100-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '八德公司簽發一張3年期、不附息、面額$2,270,000之票據，以購入公平市價為$1,800,000之土地一筆， 則該公司對二者之差價$470,000應如何處理？', '["借記「應付票據折價」，並逐年攤銷為利息費用", "借記「應付票據折價」，並逐年攤銷為土地成本之增加", "貸記「應付票據折價」，並逐年攤銷為購買土地利得", "不予處理"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "36c39c55491d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f7ba25d8d88a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "100230", "c": "602", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "100", "exam_name": "100年專技人員高考建築師、技師、第2次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01720', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-100-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '一般而言，企業為維護專利權而發生訴訟之成本，應如何處理？', '["若勝訴，則資本化；若敗訴，則列為費用", "不論勝訴或敗訴，皆列為費用", "一律資本化", "視公司政策而定"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "36c39c55491d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f7ba25d8d88a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "100230", "c": "602", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "100", "exam_name": "100年專技人員高考建築師、技師、第2次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
